title: "Counterthink" video news launched by the Health Ranger
cleaned_text:
I'm launching a new video news channel called "Counterthink," which challenges the dumbed-down status quo with intelligent, independent reporting and analysis on topics that matter for our world.

I'm launching a new video news channel called "Counterthink," which challenges the dumbed-down status quo with intelligent, independent reporting and analysis on topics that matter for our world.

"Counterthink" episodes are viewable at Counterthink.com, and one episode per week is filmed and produced at the InfoWars studios, airing at 6pm (central) on InfoWars.com. The other episodes, filmed in my own studio, are posted as they are produced, appearing at any time or day of the week (including weekends).

This first episode explores what the show is all about and hints at some of the upcoming topics to be covered.
